Second look at it, at this price it might be worth it. Similar price to the Prusa i3 FDM we were looking at and is resin. Resin is just the largest expense in these machines. Expect a couple hundred for only a couple of parts.
Waste from required cleaning/failed prints can really add up.
SLA also uses more material than FDM because it prints completely solid.
